column3: How satisfied are you with the amount of space allocated to you and your family in the camp?

column6: How satisfied are you with the quality of healthcare you and your family are receiving in the camp?
column7: How satisfied are you with the level of psychological support you and your family are receiving in the camp?
column8: How satisfied are you with the level of social support you and your family receive from neighbours and friends?
column9: Do you think you are able to exercise your religion freely in the camp?

column27: How much do you trust the NGOs in the camp?

column29: How much do you trust the Imam (religious leader)?
